---
name: Structured Output Prompt
description: A prompt that uses the GPT-4o chat API to answer questions in a structured format.
metadata:
  authors:
    - vgiraud

model:
  id: gpt-4.1
  apiType: chat

inputs:
  statement: Alice and Bob are going to a science fair on Friday.

outputs:
  name:
    kind: string
    description: The name of the event.
  date:
    kind: string
    description: The date of the event.
  location:
    kind: object
    description: The location of the event.
  activities:
    kind: array
    description: A list of activities that could take place at the event.
---
system:
Extract the event information. Also, provide a list of activities that could take place at the event.
Feel free to use creative and descriptive language to make the output engaging.
Also, feel free to make up a potential location for the event, including city, state, and country.

user:
{{statement}}